OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fwith clear spells and some hazy
OL,7,Fevening sunshine for many places. The
OL,8,Fwinds easing to light for many places.
OL,9,FMild in urban areas but notably cooler
OL,10,Fin rural spots.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FAny cloud should dissipate
OL,13,Fthroughout the morning leaving a fine
OL,14,Fday with plenty of sunshine. Feeling
OL,15,Fwarm or very warm in places with
OL,16,Ftemperatures on the rise.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
