OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FSettled and warm, with bright sunshine
OL,7,Fon Monday. Temperatures starting to
OL,8,Freduce on Tuesday and Wednesday as the
OL,9,Fwind turns onshore. Staying mostly dry
OL,10,Fwith variable amounts of cloud.
